        {
            "title": "摩根資產管理高管Michele稱市場拋售是對特朗普發出的信息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"摩根資產管理高管Michele稱市場拋售是對特朗普發出的信息\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Rq.8vW0wc4PTl1FHiAJKIw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/63113770-f673-11f0-8c37-b4f86f87536a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">摩根資產管理高管Michele稱市場拋售是對特朗普發出的信息</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
