        {
            "title": "多年爭議後英國批准中國在倫敦建設「超級大使館」 為斯塔默訪華鋪路",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 英國政府批准中國在倫敦新建大使館，結束了持續多年的拉鋸。這場爭議曾使雙邊關係出現摩擦，而此次批准也為英國首相基爾·斯塔默下周訪問北京奠定了基礎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國住房事務大臣Steve Reed在該部門網站周二發布的一項決定中表示，已「附帶條件」批准該項目。這個持續已久的審批過程曾把外界對中國的潛在安全威脅關切放到聚光燈下。該文件顯示，Reed「在做出這一決定時，已將該地點特定的國家安全因素納入考量」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-39d5dc0c-07cd-3847-9d9b-1295d8d63140-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國如今可推進在英國皇家鑄幣廠舊址上建設這個歐洲最大使館的計畫。該地塊靠近倫敦金融城。英國方面也將期待，其駐北京的使館同樣能夠取得建設發展。英國首相斯塔默計畫在本月底訪華，並與中國國家主席習近平舉行會晤。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Source: Getty Images Europe\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IaR5jvYK3pFlj6SWW3z_PQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3abeeeda8eb7c60e4d8c3cd23b1e80f8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Source: Getty Images Europe</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自中國於2018年買下倫敦塔旁的這塊地皮以來，該項目一直爭議不斷。將其建為所謂超級大使館的規劃申請多年來屢遭拖延：地方當局和政府部長在審議過程中，既要面對人權活動人士的反對，也要考慮一些人士圍繞中國打算將該建築用作間諜活動樞紐的相關擔憂，中國否認這一說法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題UK Approval of China Embassy Paves Way for Starmer Beijing Trip</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(更新文首兩段內容)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%BB%B6%E9%81%B2%E8%88%87%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E5%BE%8C-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%A8%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD-%E8%B6%85%E7%B4%9A%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A4%A8-%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-113917490.html",
