            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐洲央行總裁拉加德稱特朗普關稅威脅令不確定性捲土重來",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 歐洲央行行長拉加德表示，由於特朗普發出新的關稅威脅，不確定性已捲土重來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她在達沃斯世界經濟論壇向CNN表示，美歐之間的信任正受到破壞，並補充說兩地企業目前試圖搞清楚新關稅措施的連鎖反應。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vGXDGOesbVsGEXBNHhrhWA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/1319e5b61c3ef4d4672a9ae32f457748\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她在周二播出的這次採訪中稱：「比關稅本身更重要的是，我們再次看到不確定性上升——不確定性又回來了」。她把這些威脅形容為「我們以前看過的電影」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普可能對歐洲國家採取的行動，或將挑戰歐洲央行對未來幾年通脹和經濟活動的樂觀預期。面對日益高漲的保護主義，歐元區迄今展現出韌性，但官員們一直強調風險居高不下。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f9266aa0-5946-302f-a9ed-7fa7359151f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德表示，歐洲的政策最近變得「非常可預測」，通膨率和基準借貸成本均位於2%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">事實上，歐洲央行自6月以來一直維持利率不變，投資者和經濟學家目前均預計該行不會有進一步行動。法國央行行長Francois Villeroy de Galhau周二早些時候接受彭博電視採訪時稱，任何新關稅都須進行評估，但補充道他預計其對價格的影響「有限」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德強調，美歐之間的貿易聯繫「非常緊密」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「危及這一點，質疑這一點，對良好的商業政策無益，」她指出。「美國企業應該像歐洲企業一樣，認真思考這個問題。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB’s Lagarde Says Uncertainty Is Back Amid Latest Trump Threats</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
